<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV13">
<l>iṉṉaiyeṉṟu collalāva tillaiyātu miṭṭiṭaip</l>
<l>piṉṉaikēḷva ṉeṉparuṉpi ṇakkuṇarnta peṟṟiyōr</l>
<l>piṉṉaiyāya kōlamōṭu pērumūru mātiyum</l>
<l>niṉṉaiyār niṉaikkavallar nīrmaiyālni ṉaikkilē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing that allows [one] to say, ‘You are thus!’</l>
<l>Great people who have realized [people’s] disagreement [concerning] You</l>
<l>say that [You] are the Husband of the small-waisted Piṉṉai.</l>
<l>Then, who is capable of thinking of You, with [Your] beautiful form</l>
<l rend="indent">names, town, and the[ir] causes,</l>
<l>unless they do [so] out of [Your own] affability!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
